password &lt;em&gt;ad nauseam&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Ansible in AWS Lambda</title><link>https://www.jacoelho.com/blog/2016/02/ansible-in-aws-lambda/</link><pubDate>Thu, 18 Feb 2016 10:24:46 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.jacoelho.com/blog/2016/02/ansible-in-aws-lambda/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Originally published at &lt;a href="https://medium.com/@jacoelho/ansible-in-aws-lambda-980bb8b5791b"&gt;https://medium.com/@jacoelho/ansible-in-aws-lambda-980bb8b5791b&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>